<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.8">
<l>eṉṉai varuka veṉakkuṟittiṭ ṭiṉamalar mullaiyiṉ pantalnīḻal</l>
<l>maṉṉi yavaḷaip puṇarappukku maṟṟeṉṉaik kaṇṭuḻa ṟānekiḻntāy</l>
<l>poṉṉiṟa vāṭaiyaik kaiyiṟṟāṅkip poyyaccaṅ kāṭṭinī pōtiyēlum</l>
<l>iṉṉameṉ kaiyakat tīṅkorunāḷ varutiyē leñciṉam tīrvaṉnāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Telling me, ‘May you come,’ You entered to embrace her</l>
<l rend="indent">who stayed in the shadow of the pandal [made of] jasmine  that blossoms in clusters.</l>
<l>Afterwards, seeing me, becoming disturbed, You slipped off.</l>
<l>Even though You left holding the gold-coloured garments in [Your] hand,</l>
<l>showing false terror, I shall settle my score [with You]</l>
<l rend="indent"> if You again come within my grasp one day.</l>

      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
